casebody.head_matter:
In Re DEPARTMENT OF COMMERCE, et al., applicants.
No. 18A455.
Supreme Court of the United States
Nov. 2, 2018.
Application for stay presented to Justice GINSBURG and by her referred to the Court denied.
Justice THOMAS, Justice ALITO, and Justice GORSUCH would grant the application.
